abstract: Right-wing media have been laying the groundwork for Trump’s acquittal for half a century.
snippet: Right-wing media have been laying the groundwork for Trump’s acquittal for half a century.
lead_paragraph: If you tuned in to Fox News to watch the opening arguments of the impeachment trial on Wednesday night, you were out of luck. Oh, the trial was still technically being broadcast on the network, but it had been reduced to a muted box on the side of the screen, while Sean Hannity assured viewers, “None of this will matter.”

abstract: Surveillance capitalists control the science and the scientists, the secrets and the truth.
snippet: Surveillance capitalists control the science and the scientists, the secrets and the truth.
lead_paragraph: The debate on privacy and law at the Federal Trade Commission was unusually heated that day. Tech industry executives “argued that they were capable of regulating themselves and that government intervention would be costly and counterproductive.” Civil libertarians warned that the companies’ data capabilities posed “an unprecedented threat to individual freedom.” One observed, “We have to decide what human beings are in the electronic age. Are we just going to be chattel for commerce?” A commissioner asked, ‘‘Where should we draw the line?” The year was 1997.

abstract: One of former President Barack Obama's top fundraisers endorsed Joe Biden on Friday, a pledge of support that's likely to boost the former vice president's ability to raise cash for his 2020 campaign.
snippet: One of former President Barack Obama's top fundraisers endorsed Joe Biden on Friday, a pledge of support that's likely to boost the former vice president's ability to raise cash for his 2020 campaign.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — One of former President Barack Obama's top fundraisers endorsed Joe Biden on Friday, a pledge of support that's likely to boost the former vice president's ability to raise cash for his 2020 campaign.
headline_main: Top Obama Fundraiser Backs Biden in 2020 Contest
headline_print_headline: Top Obama Fundraiser Backs Biden in 2020 Contest

abstract: Secretary of State Mike Pompeo will visit Ukraine next week, making his first trip to the country at the heart of President Donald Trump's impeachment.

headline_print_headline: Pompeo Heads to Ukraine Next Week to Meet With President

abstract: Elizabeth Warren says she has more than 1,000 campaign staffers in 31 states and 100-plus field offices, a show of organizational strength her campaign promises will lift her to the Democratic presidential nomination and hurt President Donald Trump's chances in key battlegrounds in November.
snippet: Elizabeth Warren says she has more than 1,000 campaign staffers in 31 states and 100-plus field offices, a show of organizational strength her campaign promises will lift her to the Democratic presidential nomination and hurt President Donald Trum...
lead_paragraph: DES MOINES, Iowa — Elizabeth Warren says she has more than 1,000 campaign staffers in 31 states and 100-plus field offices, a show of organizational strength her campaign promises will lift her to the Democratic presidential nomination and hurt President Donald Trump's chances in key battlegrounds in November.
headline_main: Warren Vows Her Organization Will Win Primary, Beat Trump
headline_print_headline: Warren Vows Her Organization Will Win Primary, Beat Trump

abstract: NEW YORK — Elizabeth Warren on Friday tapped religious leaders from a variety of backgrounds to serve as an interfaith council for her presidential campaign, making her one of several Democratic contenders to invest in outreach to voters of faith.
lead_paragraph: NEW YORK — Elizabeth Warren on Friday tapped religious leaders from a variety of backgrounds to serve as an interfaith council for her presidential campaign, making her one of several Democratic contenders to invest in outreach to voters of faith.
headline_main: Warren Rolls Out Council of Interfaith Advisers
